Package: cateval
Title: Validation of Conditional Average Treatment Effects
Version: 1.5.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Pedro", "Cardoso", , "p.cardoso@exeter.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1014-9058"))
Description: Tools for validating the calibration of predicted treatment
    benefit from treatment-selection models with a continuous outcome. The
    package covers the two calibration analyses used in the validation
    procedure: overall benefit, based on matched concordant and discordant
    patients, and pairwise drug-class effects. Benefit is summarised by group
    (calibration plot), by the mean benefit of following the model, and by the
    calibration-in-the-large and calibration slope, each with analytical or
    optional pair-level bootstrap confidence intervals.
